        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "That is _not_ a \"_soft_-deprecation\" -- it will create new deprecation warnings for virtually every plugin that are hard to manage. I would strongly suggest to avoid adding a `vim.deprecate` call for at least another version or two. (Remove it from the documentation and put a `todo` comment in its place for later.)",
