        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Thanks for the feedback! I've updated the PR to remove the `vim.deprecate()` calls. \n\nNow it's a true soft-deprecation:\n- `buf` is the new preferred option (documented)\n- `buffer` still works silently (kept for backwards compat, not in docs)\n- No warnings emitted\n- Added `TODO(deprecate)` comments for future hard-deprecation in 0.15+",
